    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-special\">強化套裝風險防護系統</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">黑市改造</span>。用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 開始升級<VAL_ON>安裝程序<>。<br><br>此模組富有彈性，直到安裝完成前，確切的升級數據為<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝風險防護強度</span>。"
